Murder 360 is a true crime docuseries that uncovers ten gripping murder cases from every possible angle. Through intimate interviews, expert analysis, and rare footage, the series paints a vivid portrait of the motive, method, and aftermath of each crime — from thrill killings to deadly vows.

Stream the new Paramount+ Original docuseries premiering August 5, exclusively on Paramount+.
